REQUIREMENTS

This client requires Perl installed to run and following Perl modules:
1) Template
2) CGI::Session
3) Data::FormValidator
4) XML::Simple
5) Hash::Merge::Simple
6) Log::Log4perl
7) File::HomeDir
8) JSON
9) Devel::StackTrace
10) DateTime::Format::ISO8601
11) Term::ReadKey
12) RPC::XML
13) XML::Twig
14) IO::Socket::SSL (version 1.56)
15) LWP::Protocol::https
16) Email::Sender::Simple


On Ubuntu/Debian system, Perl is installed by default and the modules
can be installed by the following command:

    sudo apt-get install libtemplate-perl libcgi-session-perl  libdata-formvalidator-perl \
            libxml-simple-perl libhash-merge-simple-perl liblog-log4perl-perl \
            libfile-homedir-perl libjson-perl libdevel-stacktrace-perl libdatetime-format-iso8601-perl \
            libterm-readkey-perl  librpc-xml-perl libxml-twig-perl libemail-sender-perl

On other platforms the modules can be installed by CPAN utility:

    cpan -i Template

The CPAN can be used even on the Ubuntu/Debian system to upgrade Perl modules, e.g. to install
the latest version of IO::Socket::SSL:

    sudo apt-get install build-essential
    sudo cpan -i IO::Socket::SSL
